N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 21 ยง 1221.6 - Obstruction of ways, windows, doors, openings, etc. admitting air or light prohibited

State Regulations

The occupant shall not cover or obstruct in any way, windows, doorways or other openings which admit light or air into the
terminal. Notes
